Execute S:InstallAROS.cfg

GetENV DEVICE >NIL:
GetENV UNIT   >NIL:

Echo "Installation: Stage 1"
Echo "====================="
Echo ""
Echo "WARNING! WARNING WARNING! WARNING! WARNING! WARNING! WARNING! WARNING!"
Echo "This installation program will destroy all data on you harddisk!"

RequestChoice TITLE "Nuke harddisk?" BODY "Are you sure you want to destroy*Nall data on your harddisk?" GADGETS "Destroy|Abort" >ENV:CHOICE

GetENV CHOICE >NIL:
CD     T:
Touch  $CHOICE

If NOT EXISTS T:1
    Echo "Aborting..."
    Quit
Endif

Echo ""
Echo "Automatically partitioning the harddisk..."
Partition FORCE QUIET

Echo "Partitioning completed. AROS will reboot in 10 seconds."
Echo "Please execute S:InstallAROS.2 when AROS has booted again."

Wait 10 SECS
Reboot
